Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.87,0:00:05.00,statute title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(325,372)}Listopad 1993\NYokosuka
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.05,0:00:21.74,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Ty tam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.42,0:00:24.66,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Jak se jmenuješ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:27.44,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Kouichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.66,0:00:32.38,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Jestli se nepletu,\N jsi Ariake Kouichi, viď?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.12,0:00:37.06,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Trochu jsme si povídali,\N když jsem byl u vás na obědě.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:43.83,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Pamatuješ si mě?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.62,0:00:55.14,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Rád bych slyšel, \Nco se tu dnes v noci stalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.14,0:00:56.87,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Povíš mi to?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.87,0:00:58.32,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,To asi ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:00:59.25,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Je to sotva hodina.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.81,0:01:12.78,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Meteorický déšť Leonidy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.99,0:01:15.76,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Byli jste se na to podívat, ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.16,0:01:17.20,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Ano.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.49,0:01:19.63,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,S bratrem a sestrou.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.50,0:01:22.08,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,A co tvoji rodiče?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.64,0:01:24.64,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Chtěli jsme jít tajně,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:26.60,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,ale bratr se podřekl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.65,0:01:28.80,RnK thought/past 2nd person,,0,0,0,,Samotné děti v noci venku?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.80,0:01:29.79,RnK thought/past 2nd person,,0,0,0,,Co když se vám něco stane?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.79,0:01:31.54,RnK thought/past 2nd person,,0,0,0,,Nikdo neumřel na to, \Nže neviděl padat hvězdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.39,0:01:33.16,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,A pak?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.51,0:01:35.62,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Nechtěli jsme to jen tak vzdát.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.62,0:01:37.96,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Vyplížili jsme se v noci ven.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.45,0:01:39.80,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Kolik asi bylo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.65,0:01:42.07,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Kolem půlnoci.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:44.74,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Vaši rodiče spali?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.26,0:01:49.10,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,V pokoji o něčem mluvili.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:51.04,RnK thought/past 2nd person,,0,0,0,,Co je?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.64,0:01:52.34,RnK thought/past 2nd person,,0,0,0,,Máš porno časopisy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:54.24,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Máš porno časopisy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:01:56.62,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Asi protože...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.06,0:02:00.75,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,jsem schovával za zády naše boty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:01.77,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:04.31,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Nebylo tam nic neobvyklého?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.94,0:02:08.82,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Mamka...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:12.52,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,myslím, že trochu plakala.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.56,0:02:15.38,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,To se občas stávalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:17.61,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Někdy se s taťkou hádali.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:23.16,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Mluvili asi o něčem, o čem\N nechtěli mluvit před námi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:24.40,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,O obchodu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.40,0:02:25.13,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:27.96,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Mohl bych už jít?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:29.12,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Jsi unavený?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:30.62,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,To ne, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.32,0:02:33.32,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Můj bráška a sestřička...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:36.53,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Jděte je zkontrolovat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:47.05,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Vzal jsi boty \Na odešel po schodech.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:49.97,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Vylezli jste oknem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:52.14,RnK thought/past 2nd person,,0,0,0,,Zapomeňte, když prší.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:53.47,RnK thought/past 2nd person,,0,0,0,,Přestává.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.47,0:02:55.66,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Viděli jste padat hvězdy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:55.66,RnK thought/past 2nd person,,0,0,0,,- Koukněte na to!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.66,0:02:56.88,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Bylo to hezké?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.29,0:03:01.82,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Potom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:03.93,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,v kolik jste šli zpátky?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:07.40,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Asi kolem druhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:09.66,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Sestřička spala,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.95,0:03:10.61,RnK thought/past 2nd person,,0,0,0,,Mám ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.61,0:03:12.78,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,proto se do patra\N oknem vlézt nedalo,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:14.63,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,tak jsme šli restaurací.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.89,0:03:18.59,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Bylo tam zhasnuto,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:21.08,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,tak jsem si myslel, že už spí.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.69,0:03:26.84,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Dveře do pokoje byly\N otevřené a svítilo se tam.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:29.50,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Napadlo mě, že jsme v průšvihu,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.11,0:03:32.66,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,že se vzbudili a čekají na nás.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:42.74,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Nohy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:47.37,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Zdálo se mi divné, \Nže by spala v ponožkách.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:49.80,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Proto...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.57,0:03:54.13,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,jsem si myslel, že nespí.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.63,0:04:11.48,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Pak jsi zavolal 110.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.05,0:04:15.07,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Čekali jste,\Naž přijedeme, ano?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:18.37,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Promiň, vím, že jsi\N unavený, ale jinak to nejde.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.37,0:04:19.37,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Pane Kashiwabaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:21.69,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Promiň na chvíli.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.71,0:04:27.36,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Co je s nimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:31.03,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Sestřička...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:31.72,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Shizuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:34.27,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Shizuna spí.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:35.20,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,A Taisuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:37.05,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:39.45,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,ze šoku nemluví.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:42.28,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Počkej tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:45.37,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Musíme prohlédnout i první patro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,0:04:47.98,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Potřebujeme mít \Nty místnosti prázdné.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:50.38,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Přiveď oba dolů.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.03,0:04:57.70,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Je trochu škoda ji budit, viď?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:05:01.89,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Bylo by to jedno,\N kdyby se nic nestalo,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.27,0:05:05.24,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,ale dneska,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:08.74,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,když se stalo tohle,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:10.53,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,chtěl bych, \Nabyste ji nechali spát.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:12.18,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Myslím, že Shii...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.73,0:05:14.81,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,je moc malá,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:16.49,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,a nic neví.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:19.78,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Vůbec neví, co se stalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:22.97,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Proto může klidně spát.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:25.74,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,To je poslední noc,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:28.40,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,kdy může takhle spát.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.15,0:05:32.42,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Zítra...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:35.78,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,se to všechno dozví.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.01,0:05:39.76,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Ale teď,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:49.05,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,teď ji chci nechat spát.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:55.26,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Já ti rozumím.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:05:59.05,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Necháme ji spát,\N dokud se neprobudí.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:03.74,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Jen protože jsme\N chtěli vidět hvězdy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.93,0:06:07.78,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Protože jsme chtěli\N vidět padat hvězdy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.32,0:06:10.45,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Všechno jen protože...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:12.05,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Na to vůbec nemysli.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:14.38,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Kdybyste byli zůstali doma...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:15.33,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Hagimuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:20.63,RnK thought/past,,0,0,0,,Jen protože...
